Template: worker/server_ip
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: Server IP address for client connections
 Enter the IP address that clients will use to connect to the Worker service.
 .
 This should be the IP address that clients can reach:
  - Local network: 192.168.1.100, 10.0.1.100, etc.
  - Public IP: Your server's public IP address
  - Default: Uses auto-detected IP from your network interface
 .
 The service will bind to this IP address and generate SSL certificates
 that are valid for this IP.